[
  {"text": "小红帽", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "从前，在一个美丽的小村庄里，住着一个可爱的小女孩。她总是戴着一顶红色的帽子，所以大家都叫她小红帽。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "有一天，妈妈对小红帽说：", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "小红帽，奶奶生病了，你去给她送些点心和葡萄酒吧。记住，走大路，不要在森林里逗留。", "role": "mother", "voice_id": "female-chengshu", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "好的，妈妈，我会小心的！", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "小红帽高兴地回答。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "小红帽提着篮子，蹦蹦跳跳地向奶奶家走去。奶奶住在村外的森林里，要走很长一段路。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "走着走着，小红帽遇到了一只大灰狼。大灰狼装出一副和善的样子问道：", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "小姑娘，你要去哪里呀？", "role": "wolf", "voice_id": "male-qn-badao", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "我去奶奶家，给她送点心和葡萄酒，她生病了。", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "小红帽天真地回答。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "你奶奶住在哪里呀？", "role": "wolf", "voice_id": "male-qn-badao", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "大灰狼眼珠一转，假装关心地问。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "就在森林那边，三棵大橡树下面的那栋小房子。", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "大灰狼心里暗暗盘算着坏主意，它对小红帽说：", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "小红帽，你看森林里有多少美丽的花啊！你为什么不采一些送给奶奶呢？", "role": "wolf", "voice_id": "male-qn-badao", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "小红帽看了看四周，果然有很多漂亮的野花。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "对呀！奶奶一定会喜欢这些花的！", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "于是小红帽离开大路，跑进森林里去采花。而大灰狼却飞快地跑向奶奶的小屋。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "大灰狼来到奶奶家门口，轻轻地敲了敲门。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "是谁呀？", "role": "grandma", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Kind-hearted_Elder", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "奶奶虚弱地问。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "是我，小红帽。我给您送点心和葡萄酒来了。", "role": "wolf", "voice_id": "male-qn-badao", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "大灰狼捏着嗓子假装小红帽的声音说。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "拉一下门闩就能进来了，我没力气起来开门。", "role": "grandma", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Kind-hearted_Elder", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "大灰狼拉开门闩，冲进屋里，一口把奶奶吞进了肚子里。然后，它穿上奶奶的衣服，戴上奶奶的帽子，躺在床上，拉上窗帘，等着小红帽。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "不一会儿，小红帽采了满满一束花，来到奶奶家。她轻轻推开门，走了进去。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "奶奶，您好些了吗？", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "小红帽走近床边，觉得奶奶今天看起来很奇怪。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "奶奶，您的耳朵怎么这么大呀？", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "那是为了更好地听你说话呀，孩子。", "role": "wolf", "voice_id": "male-qn-badao", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "奶奶，您的眼睛怎么这么大呀？", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "那是为了更好地看清你呀，孩子。", "role": "wolf", "voice_id": "male-qn-badao", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "奶奶，您的嘴巴怎么这么大呀？", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "那是为了更好地吃掉你呀！", "role": "wolf", "voice_id": "male-qn-badao", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "大灰狼说着，从床上跳起来，把小红帽也吞进了肚子里。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "吃饱了的大灰狼又躺回床上，很快就打起了呼噜，而且声音越来越响。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "正好一位猎人从屋外经过，他听到了很响的呼噜声，心想：", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "老奶奶怎么打这么响的呼噜？我得进去看看她是不是出什么事了。", "role": "hunter", "voice_id": "male-qn-jingying", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "猎人推门进去一看，床上躺着的竟然是大灰狼！", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "原来你在这儿，你这个坏家伙！我找你好久了！", "role": "hunter", "voice_id": "male-qn-jingying", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "猎人正要开枪，忽然想到大灰狼可能吞掉了奶奶。于是他拿出剪刀，小心地剪开大灰狼的肚子。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "剪了几下，他看到了红色的帽子，再剪几下，小红帽跳了出来。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "啊，里面太黑了，吓死我了！", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "接着，奶奶也被救了出来，虽然有些虚弱，但还活着。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "小红帽赶紧跑出去搬来几块大石头，塞进大灰狼的肚子里。大灰狼醒来想逃跑，却因为肚子里的石头太重，扑通一声摔倒在地，再也爬不起来了。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "奶奶吃了小红帽带来的点心，喝了葡萄酒，精神好多了。小红帽心里暗暗发誓：", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "我以后再也不离开大路跑进森林了。", "role": "little_red", "voice_id": "lovely_girl", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "从此以后，小红帽牢牢记住了这个教训，再也没有不听妈妈的话。", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""},
  {"text": "故事讲完了。小朋友们，你们也要记住，一定要听爸爸妈妈的话，不要轻易相信陌生人哦！", "role": "narrator", "voice_id": "Chinese (Mandarin)_Gentleman", "emotion": ""}
]
